---
import Link from "../../Link.astro";
---

<section
  class="container rounded-xl mx-auto mb-8 bg-dark-500 border border-t border-b border-secondary-300"
  id="location"
>
  <div class="p-10">
    <h2 class="mb-8 text-2xl font-bold text-secondary-200">
      Location and travel info
    </h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 font-semibold">
      <div>
        <h3 class="mb-4 text-xl font-bold text-primary-200">Event Venues</h3>
        <h4 class="mb-4 text-lg font-bold text-secondary-200">
          Conference Day
        </h4>
        <p class="mb-4">
          The conference will be held at [MAIN VENUE NAME]. It's located in [AREA DESCRIPTION], convenient for attendees and close to local attractions.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4">Address: [MAIN VENUE ADDRESS]</p>
        <Link
          href="[GOOGLE MAPS LINK TO MAIN VENUE]"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          target="_blank"
        >
          [View on Google Maps]
        </Link>

        <h4 class="mb-4 mt-10 text-lg font-bold text-secondary-200">
          Workshops and pre-conference events
        </h4>
        <p class="mb-4">
          The workshops and pre-conference events will be held at [SECONDARY VENUE NAME]. This venue is [BRIEF DESCRIPTION OF SECONDARY VENUE].
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4">Address: [SECONDARY VENUE ADDRESS]</p>
        <Link
          href="[GOOGLE MAPS LINK TO SECONDARY VENUE]"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          target="_blank"
        >
          [View on Google Maps]
        </Link>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="mb-4 text-xl font-bold text-primary-200">Getting there</h3>
        <p class="mb-4">
          [CITY NAME] is well-connected to major cities, with regular flights to and from the [AIRPORT NAME].
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4">
          The conference venue is easily accessible by public transportation, with several [TRANSPORTATION OPTIONS] available.
        </p>
        <Link
          href="[AIRPORT WEBSITE]"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          target="_blank"
        >
          [[AIRPORT NAME]]
        </Link>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
